    "name": "Silicium",
    "steam_appid": 3048990,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048990/extras/3412b07a1d3f441c6d1c454eaf1183e2.avif?t=1767440019\" width=1188 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Silicium is an uncompromising survival game where you play a disposable mining robot on a hostile planet. Mine, refine and automate. Export your quota for corporate or die trying. Play solo, co-op or join ruthless 24/7 PvP servers. Unlock new blueprints each run and try again with new possibilities. <br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EXTRACT</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extract precious resources to craft new items. Each resource requires the proper tool to be mined. Upgrade your gear to reach the most valuable mineral of all: Silicium.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048990/extras/dd95dccdd53ff166d5c5341e0468b6a7.poster.avif?t=1767440019\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048990/extras/dd95dccdd53ff166d5c5341e0468b6a7.webm?t=1767440019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048990/extras/dd95dccdd53ff166d5c5341e0468b6a7.mp4?t=1767440019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><strong>BUILD</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your base to secure your loot and defend against enemies. Level up to learn crafting recipes of items and structures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048990/extras/4b0dbffe064b42ae21385dc9e5366e57.poster.avif?t=1767440019\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048990/extras/4b0dbffe064b42ae21385dc9e5366e57.webm?t=1767440019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048990/extras/4b0dbffe064b42ae21385dc9e5366e57.mp4?t=1767440019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EXPORT</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Launch transport rockets to export ores into space and get your paycheck. Craft smelting equipment to refine ores for higher value and improved efficiency.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048990/extras/196a9be264099be6b662e90c4f93331f.poster.avif?t=1767440019\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048990/extras/196a9be264099be6b662e90c4f93331f.webm?t=1767440019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048990/extras/196a9be264099be6b662e90c4f93331f.mp4?t=1767440019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EXPLORE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the planet to scavenge abandoned mining sites. But beware, corrupted mining drones have turned hostile and attack without warning.    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048990/extras/e39664f21ba8376d2a3de68758d2ecc7.poster.avif?t=1767440019\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048990/extras/e39664f21ba8376d2a3de68758d2ecc7.webm?t=1767440019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048990/extras/e39664f21ba8376d2a3de68758d2ecc7.mp4?t=1767440019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>COMPETE</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo or compete in public PvP servers where the action never stops. Can you outsmart the competition and extract the most resources? </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death means starting over, but your earnings unlock new crafting recipes for your next run. No persistent bases. No offline raids. Every session is a fresh battle for survival where only active players compete.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048990/extras/ed84a7da329db049347ad5fed1ffc75d.poster.avif?t=1767440019\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048990/extras/ed84a7da329db049347ad5fed1ffc75d.webm?t=1767440019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048990/extras/ed84a7da329db049347ad5fed1ffc75d.mp4?t=1767440019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
